data.description: Fully renovated by previous owner and wonderfully maintained by current owners, check out this fully updated home in a quiet cut-de-sac by the water. All kitchen appliances, water heater and flooring are less than 2 years old. Washer and dryer convey with property. Relax on the back covered porch and snag this one up in time for summer.
